Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.01,0:01:35.60,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上课中拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Attack！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.89,0:01:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做这种事情你父母会伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.62,0:01:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖地还我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有前途的年青人在过程中不能留下污点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你了解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.59,0:02:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让我发挥实力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是不讲理的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下分你骨头吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在早晨练球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依旧那么精力充沛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在友引高中就职
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:02:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通称温泉标识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,35岁 单身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他将在一生中一直回想这个最倒霉的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天妇罗面来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要让我等几小时才甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的店是要让客人吃像乌龙面的拉面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你玩笑开的真大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才过了五分钟而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想是应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我等这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以让我到月底才付钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正从一开始叫时就打算这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来拿粉笔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就放在那边 自己拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了不能给你这个面之外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的就自己拿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在现在这个时候吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 喔 不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在是空堂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了下节课
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 还好 要吃一口吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那是什么眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说什么就说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我并不是对校长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打扰你吃饭时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年四班好像问题很多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实从家长会和教育会都有怨言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师是位诚实的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很尽力在教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:05:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然到现在都由我在中间调解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是比起海鲜拉面还是吃不习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这空肠虚脱感换成了心情不好及你这种样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 渐渐热起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之对付那些顽童 身体情况一定会变差的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够的话一定要按时吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够了解我的只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能这样当我的顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我唯一在学校心中的安慰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱花老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由好色的心产生\N极度的迷乱和因日常生活不节制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而产生的缺钱病
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:05:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切记千万不要往邪道去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 樱花老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚的你们都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准看 不准看 到那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再看就揍你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以随便乱丢药瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这样学生才会藐视你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶劣的心情转换而成为愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的温泉有点怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是不是有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲求不满 欲求不满
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样根本没人嫁他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛肉饭一大碗再加榨菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还在这里混
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:06:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了这种地步还要挣扎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 再走就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 牛肉饭店并不是操场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在很赶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被你撞到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把放在口中嚼味的牛肉吞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 给这位一个大碗的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附加蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出手很大方嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一碗牛肉饭 你看轻它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常是三百元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大碗再加蛋顶多只是四百五十元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想用那么便宜的东西逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很划算对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:08:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我绝没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快 便宜 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这牛肉饭的三大原则
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要现在就修正
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为美味因为好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才决定奉献我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是因为快或便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的假牛肉饭迷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我一生的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不敢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你浪费了我宝贵的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又破坏了牛肉饭的名誉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这罪行万世都会得到惩罚的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这天对他来说就像十三号星期五
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及佛灭 三怜亡 天诛杀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1999年第七个月为止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气浓缩为一日之最惨的一日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的五个人站住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时他那愤怒的心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐形成了一个很大的决心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们下次再翘课的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就准备补习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是当真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是开玩笑那他的演技太真了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他一定会做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他眼中闪出了真实的光耀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以让补习牺牲宝贵的假期到来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补习是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我也没关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补习是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因各种事情都破坏了上课
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照那样如果再破坏一定会补习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 补习是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很不甘心但也只好认真上课
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总比假日时来学校好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补习是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这顽童
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢打我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕到后面去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 高中生欺负幼儿不觉得羞耻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候才装成幼儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在什么也不知下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉醉于一时胜利的阿当一行人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而开始了可怕的一个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在开始上课前告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你们三分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量讲个够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想安静地上课
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有一个人敢乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不上课立即补习
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是蛮横不讲理的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常吵闹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在教师开宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把墙壁弄坏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛也进来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天花板 地板都弄破洞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他想数都数不完
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直不断地破坏上课
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再违反一律补习
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.09,0:11:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是威胁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一讲话就补习
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 补习是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在假日上课
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想补习
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗 拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也绝对不能讲话 是为了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了达令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我绝对不讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三分钟经过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次就好 好希望上像这样的课
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始上课
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课本第97页
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来报仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To加动词的原形
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时有名词形容词的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称此为不定词
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不定词无主语
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不会受人称 复数而变形
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此有名词用法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to buy it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经想买它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此安静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从开始教书这十三年中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次尝到如此的优越感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后有敬称语用法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no books to read
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.15,0:12:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这里请诸星同学来翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请诸星同学来翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请诸星同学来翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来 诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说请你翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因不能讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道就回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作梦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我们说话而来补习
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会受骗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是陷阱绝对不要说话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 好好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关上课的可以说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你们竟然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:13:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就彻底地来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在连讲话都不允许了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发出一点声音就立刻补习
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚竟敢如此待我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来打你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 现在是上课中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来报仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负可怜的幼儿下场是如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们身体都不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是教室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老伯 你在那边东张西望站着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老伯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说继续上课吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想依照这个状况能上课吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打呀 打呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真感动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么珍惜我的课吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么讨厌补习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续上课
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢戏弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反击是不可原谅的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是来打架的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没用也抵抗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话啊 最近的幼儿脾气是很坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不满就去跟阿当说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都怎么了 生病了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不太对劲 到底怎么了？真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 绝对不要说话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 达令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:17:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用眼睛对话好像一对夫妻似的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 叫那孩子出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要受骗 拉姆 是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别允许你说话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以叫他出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都漠视我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就应该如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着看下面的课文
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生气了 真的生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 终于开始有劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.36,0:18:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想装蒜也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有没有怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吗？喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续上课 拒绝补习
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在非常猛烈地燃烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是学生的榜样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许以前我都看错了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里我也要重生而加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 要继续上课
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 谁借我课本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不够 现在才开始好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AH-1对地攻击直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做的真好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干吧 打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小天 做的太过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:20:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是如此忍耐着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 小天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别得意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们认为这样就完了\N那实在是大错特错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:21:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 天战士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.88,0:22:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆姐也有错啊
